{"tid":1200874,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【逃犯條例】外交部：中央繼續支持特區政府修例","createTime":"2019-06-11T00:32:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T01:13:30.000Z","uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"53c8debd3e51c951cc3c5703b8d8d4eb6e4274f7","tid":1200874,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T00:32:18.000Z","msg":"【逃犯條例】外交部：中央繼續支持特區政府修例<br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】外交部發言人重申中央政府繼續支持特區政府修訂逃犯條例的工作。 <br />\n<br />\n外交部發言人耿爽：「<span style=\"color: red;\">特區政府給出的數字不是一百萬，是比這個少得多的數字，我在這裏不願意跟你進入到細節的討論當中，但你所謂的哪個數字大，哪個數字多就證明誰代表民意，我覺得這並沒有說服力</span>，香港回歸之後一國兩制、港人治港的方針得到切實的貫徹落實，香港市民的各項合法權益都得到充分保障，香港市民亦有切實的體會，國際社會也有公論，所以我不知道你所謂的一國兩制沒有得到很多貫徹落實，這個說法是從何而來。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=351212&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D351212%26refer%3DShare&d=bDeBUyUVyPRGeZhx3zx6lTDyw%2Fr9SRfH8QBX8OZV2FM%3D&h=1e161cf4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D351212%26refer%3DShare&h=b3ce6b12\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=351212&amp;refer=Share</a>"},{"pid":"1a8e0839689e955818fdab3030efec870ef4fe37","tid":1200874,"uid":14816,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T00:34:00.000Z","msg":"你支共唔會死多過35人添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1028fbc3a14f577d1701901139ac4eeda24b34eb","tid":1200874,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T00:36:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c27e5694e5a013e59b12fc940d8f0364faa34db9","tid":1200874,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T00:39:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被